  <P>Each primary key column description has the following columns:
   <OL>
 	<LI><B>PKTABLE_CAT</B> String => primary key table catalog
       being imported (may be null)
 	<LI><B>PKTABLE_SCHEM</B> String => primary key table schema
       being imported (may be null)
